In front of us, on higher ground, at a distance of some three hundred feet, a pine forest began. I looked at it and … well, I can swear that I felt as if I had known it already. Yes, that’s it, now I am getting it clear—I certainly did have that queer sensation; it has not been added as an aftertouch. And that yellow post … How meaningly it looked at me, when I glanced back—as if it were saying: “I am here, I am at your service.…” And those pines f